overhead.description: Wages (other than casual included in activity budgets)
overhead.name: wages

tclui.name: Manager X
tclui.rule:
if (available('tractor=t1,implement=p1')) THEN
if (paddock_is_fallow() = 1 and FallowIn <> 'yes' and (NextCrop = 0 or NextCrop = '[crop]')) then if (date_within('[date1], [date2]') = 1) then if (rain[[rainnumdays]] >= [raincrit] AND esw >= [esw_amount] ) <> 0) OR ('[must_sow]' = 'yes' AND today = date('[date2]'))) THEN ChooseNextCrop = 'yes' ! for rotations
economics expenditure type = seedcost, name = [crop], rate = 120 (kg/ha), area = 200 (ha)
[crop] sow plants =[density], sowing_depth = [depth], cultivar = [cultivar], row_spacing = [row_spacing], crop_class = [class]
endif if today = date('[date2]') then ChooseNextCrop = 'yes' endif endif endif
ENDIF

if [crop].stage_name = 'harvest_ripe' or [crop].plant_status = 'dead' then
economics expenditure type = contract, name = broadacre_harvesting, rate = 1, area = 200 (ha)
[crop] harvest [crop] end_crop endif

economics expenditure type = fertilisercost, name = [fert_type_sow], rate = [fert_amount_sow], area = 200 (ha) [fertmodule] apply amount = [fert_amount_sow] (kg/ha), depth = 50 (mm), type = [fert_type_sow]
